4cwh3y70p6fdb select a.tablespace_name, a.meg, a.maxmeg, a.file_name, a.file_id, a.ts#, a.blocksize, a.flag, b.freebytes, b.maxfreebytes, nvl(c.ts#, -99) from (select f.tablespace_name, (f.bytes)/1048576 meg, (f.maxbytes)/1048576 maxmeg, f.file_name, f.file_id, ts.ts#, ts.blocksize, DECODE(BITAND(ts.flags, 3), 1, ts.dflminlen, 0) flag from sys.ts$ ts, sys.dba_data_files f where ts.contents$ = 0 and ts.online$ = 1 AND ( ts.bitmapped = 0 OR (ts.bitmapped != 0 AND bitand(ts.flags, 3) = 0)) AND bitand(flags, 2048) != 2048 and f.tablespace_name = ts.name) a, (SELECT ts.name tablespace_name, SUM(e.length * ts.blocksize/1048576) freebytes, MAX(e.length * ts.blocksize/1024) maxfreebytes FROM sys.fet$ e, sys.ts$ ts WHERE ts.ts# = e.ts# GROUP BY ts.name UNION ALL SELECT ts.name tablespace_name, SUM(e.blocks * ts.blocksize/1048576) freebytes, MAX(e. blocks * ts.blocksize/1024) maxfreebytes FROM sys.dba_lmt_free_space e, sys.ts$ ts WHERE ts.ts# = e.tablespace_id GROUP BY ts.name) b, (select distinct s.ts# from sys.seg$ s where s.maxexts < 2100000000 and s.maxexts - extents < 2 and exists (select 1 from sys.sys_objects so where so.header_block = s.block# and s.file# = so.header_file and s.ts# = so.ts_number)) c where a.tablespace_name = b.tablespace_name and a.ts# = c.ts#(+) order by a.tablespace_name, a.file_name
